{"tid":1944504,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港姑娘教支那狗嚟香港搶資源","createTime":"2020-03-26T12:14:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T13:13:00.000Z","uid":160314,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"3aca31f6f9e36d1c43d8f8b98837591b086d75e1","tid":1944504,"uid":160314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T12:14:13.000Z","msg":"屌那星！自己係蝗蟲已經算，仲要教鳩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有網友起底揾到尼位小姐姐診所，大家請留意唔好幫襯尼間診所 請埋啲大陸臭西做姑娘！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港方健醫療中心<br />\n尖沙咀廣東道30號新港中心一座502室<br />\n自稱普通話最好既香港姑娘<br />\n教大陸人落黎睇醫生同拎綜援福利<br />\n應該多數專做大陸人生意<br />\n千其唔好去<br />\n<br />\n診所FB<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/hkfortresshealth/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fhkfortresshealth%2F&d=NMuDHS38lj0XaiXuPCYWR9%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=493586fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/hkfortresshealth/</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個大陸女人微博 教大陸人拎著數<br />\n<a href=\"https://weibo.com/u/5534209314\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fweibo.com%2Fu%2F5534209314&d=NMuDHS38lj0XaiXuPCYWR9%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=90d45ba5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://weibo.com/u/5534209314</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vw5RaM3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvw5RaM3.jpg&h=3676cc86&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/adty8yK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fadty8yK.png&h=064bdd55&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p1cstyL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp1cstyL.jpg&h=80a23